<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_350" id="174r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_350_r1l4">Den von Meincʒ </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_350_r1l5"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / als wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> botten auf eẅr ſchrıft <expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan> nehſt <expan>u<ex>er</ex>gang<ex>en</ex></expan> ſamſtag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r1l6">ein antwurt geben <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ wır auf dıe ʒeıt nıht <expan>treffenlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> meͣre </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r1l7">weſten etc Alſo tun wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>ʒuwıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ ſeıd einem bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r1l9">vns komen ıſt / ein ſchrıft Von 
<add><ab facs="#facs_350_r1l8">gelegenheıt </ab></add> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> gnedıgıſten <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ des Römi = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r1l10">ſchen etc künıgs / vnd auch der lewfft <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu Beheım / dıeſelben </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r1l11">ſchrıft er vns geweıſet hat / der wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> in <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r1l12">ein <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> <expan>hıerynn<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>verſloſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r1l13">lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_350" id="174r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Meincz</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als wir
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> botten auf ewr
                                                schrift <expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>nehstv<ex>er</ex>gang<ex>en</ex></expan>
                                                samstag ein antwurt geben
                                                  <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir auf die
                                                zeit niht <expan>treffenlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
                                                meͣre westen etc., also tun wir
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>zu wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz seid einem
                                                bey uns komen ist ein schrift von
                                                  <add>gelegenheit</add>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> gnedigisten
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des römischen etc.
                                                künigs und auch der lewfft
                                                  <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> zu Beheim, dieselben
                                                schrift er uns geweiset hat, der wir
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> in
                                                  <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> ein
                                                  <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan>
<expan>hierynn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>versloss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb
                                                  <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                                  <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
